    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The Long Island Rail Road’s Waverly station opened in 1843, later renamed Holtsville in the 1890s after farmers complained about misdirected shipments.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        4,
        5
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Holtsville%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The LIRR station closed in 1998, leaving Ronkonkoma and Medford as the nearest stops for the CDP.",
